      <span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_review_2033143515'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it gr-button gr-button--small" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F17969995-john-smith---last-known-survivor-of-the-microsoft-wars">Like</a></span>
