<span id="freeTextContainer6564888448349017232">This was an interesting book. I didn&apos;t care for the format - interview style/dialogue through out - but it worked for the telling of the story. It is a story about what happens when the world as we know ends, its rebuilding, and interesting concepts on why it ended to begin with. </span>
  <span id="freeText6564888448349017232" style="display:none">This was an interesting book. I didn't care for the format - interview style/dialogue through out - but it worked for the telling of the story. It is a story about what happens when the world as we know ends, its rebuilding, and interesting concepts on why it ended to begin with. </span>
  <a data-text-id="6564888448349017232" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

